  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 13 SECONDS] In, in, when you, when you asked me before, did I experience anti-Semitism, in, in August, 1934, after I had passed my final examinations and graduated-- by the way, with a certificate of excellence from the European Fashion Academy-- was the only student there and the only Jew who got this, some Nazis who were in our workshop and tried to sabotage me any-- in many, many different ways-- did not get it.",
      "word_count": 77
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this is a little bit fitting in with what I said just a few moments ago.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I, I got a job in Hamburg with one of the fine tailoring firms in Hamburg, [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Christian ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Ohlmeyer. ?] And I started with them on the first of August, 1934.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the business manager of this firm was a Nazi, a uniformed Nazi.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the designer I worked for was an SS  man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Piotrowski was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We used to call him Pios.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And Piotrowski, after I started there, and I went to Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Ohlmeyer-- ?] his name was [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Christian ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Ohlmeyer, ?] who was a friend of my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I got this job partly because of this interrelationship between people who own businesses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And, And I went to Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Ohlmeyer ?] and said, you know, I forgot, when I first met you, I forgot to tell you that I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He said, I knew that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He said, you know-- I said, well, I thought you should know that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he said, well, you know, he said, I wouldn't necessarily go into the workshop and say what you just told me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They don't have to know it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Ohlmeyter, ?] I will not go and say I am a Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But I will never deny it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I remember that a couple of-- maybe two months after I started there, and in the meantime, we were in the workshop.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were grouped together, together with this designer, Piotrowski.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And one day, Piotrowski came back to the workshop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And he had tried on a suit on the man who was a South American of an old patrician importing/exporting family in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And he was dark skinned and dark haired.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he didn't like what Piotrowski tried on him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And Piotrowski was full of anger when he came back into the shop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And he took the garment and threw it in the corner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And he said, that damn Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I couldn't satisfy him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And, and I looked at Piotrowski.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And by that time, we had met many, many times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we knew each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And we used to walk home together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And I said to him, Pios, he is, he is not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "He said, of course he's a Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I said, no he isn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "He's, he's a South American.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I said, I happen to know the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "He is  not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, well, what difference does it make?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why do you defend him?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I'm not defending him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm defending myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he looked at me and said, you are not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, I'm not the type of Jew that you see in the which was the, the wildest, almost pornographic, antisemitic newspaper published by Julius Streicher.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, he said, I know a Jew when I see one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, do you really?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, well, you saw me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you met me eight weeks ago.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you never discovered that I was Jewish until I told you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, when you think of the Olympic games, there is a woman, Helene Mayer, who is, won the gold medal in fencing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, don't tell me she's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, she's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, the things that you are being taught are not quite right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't you see it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would take this attitude wherever I could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Pios and I got along the whole period I was in Hamburg working for him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was somehow the same kind of philosophy that made me tell Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wendel about my experiences in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At any point during the '30s, did you start experiencing fear of what was happening around you?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I experienced deep fear, tremendous fear, when the Gestapo came on the 9th of November-- the night from the 9th or the 10th of November-- and arrested us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1938.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I would like to go back for a moment, before I get to Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By, in May, 1938, we were still in business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had, at one of the most prominent corners in downtown Hildesheim, there was this store with six large windows, [INAUDIBLE] windows, and a business that had flourished.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Nazis became kind of desperate.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
